  <!-- EN: ChiYou flame halberd【First-rate】 -->
  <RI_Weapon_ChiYouFlameHalberd.label>蚩尤怒炎戟【一品】</RI_Weapon_ChiYouFlameHalberd.label>
  <!-- EN: 【First-rate】Melee weapon\n\nA long halberd with violent power, the whole body constantly spewing fire. The halberd is said to have been inspired by the ancient myth of Chiyou, the warrior master, whose anger still burns bright and gushes out through the halberd. -->
  <RI_Weapon_ChiYouFlameHalberd.description>【一品】近战兵器\n\n一把具有暴戾力量的长戟，周身不断冒出火舌。这把长戟据说灵感来自远古时期的神话，兵主蚩尤，他的怒火依旧熊熊燃烧，并通过长戟喷涌而出。</RI_Weapon_ChiYouFlameHalberd.description>
  <!-- EN: 蚩尤怒炎 -->
  <RI_Weapon_ChiYouFlameHalberd.comps.CompEquippableAbilityReloadable.chargeNoun>十字怒炎</RI_Weapon_ChiYouFlameHalberd.comps.CompEquippableAbilityReloadable.chargeNoun>
  <!-- EN: on cooldown -->
  <RI_Weapon_ChiYouFlameHalberd.comps.CompEquippableAbilityReloadable.cooldownGerund>冷却中</RI_Weapon_ChiYouFlameHalberd.comps.CompEquippableAbilityReloadable.cooldownGerund>
  <!-- EN: 戟刃 -->
  <RI_Weapon_ChiYouFlameHalberd.tools.0.label>戟刃</RI_Weapon_ChiYouFlameHalberd.tools.0.label>
  <!-- EN: 戟尖 -->
  <RI_Weapon_ChiYouFlameHalberd.tools.1.label>戟尖</RI_Weapon_ChiYouFlameHalberd.tools.1.label>
  
  <!-- EN: Dragon pattern stick【First-rate】 -->
  <RI_Weapon_DragonPatternStick.label>盘龙通天棍【一品】</RI_Weapon_DragonPatternStick.label>
  <!-- EN: 【First-rate】Melee weapon\n\nA long stick with the power of god, although this stick can not be free to grow or shrink, but with each stroke, it can make the earth tremble, and with each sweep, it can tear the air. -->
  <RI_Weapon_DragonPatternStick.description>【一品】近战兵器\n\n一根具有通天伟力的长棍，虽然这根棍子无法做到自由变大缩小，但是其每次敲击，都能令大地颤抖，每次横扫，都能撕裂空气。</RI_Weapon_DragonPatternStick.description>
  <!-- EN: 千钧断岳 -->
