  <!-- EN: Glass pearl umbrella【First-rate】 -->
  <RI_Weapon_GlassPearlUmbrella.label>琉璃珍珠伞【一品】</RI_Weapon_GlassPearlUmbrella.label>
  <!-- EN: 【First-rate】Melee weapon\n\nThis is not a weapon of great destructive power, but it has powerful healing abilities. It is said that a practitioner once walked the earth, holding her umbrella aloft. The faint green light that emanated from the umbrella healed all the people who had been tortured by war into unrecognizable shapes. She was revered as a goddess and a temple was built in her honor. -->
  <RI_Weapon_GlassPearlUmbrella.description>【一品】近战兵器\n\n这并不是一柄杀伤力强大的武器，但具有强大的治愈能力。相传，曾有一名修炼者步行人间，她举起伞，伞洒下淡淡绿光，将因为战乱被折磨得不成人形的人们通通治愈。而她也被尊为天仙，立庙供奉。</RI_Weapon_GlassPearlUmbrella.description>
  <!-- EN: 琉璃珠光术 -->
  <RI_Weapon_GlassPearlUmbrella.comps.CompEquippableAbilityReloadable.chargeNoun>琉璃珠光</RI_Weapon_GlassPearlUmbrella.comps.CompEquippableAbilityReloadable.chargeNoun>
  <!-- EN: on cooldown -->
  <RI_Weapon_GlassPearlUmbrella.comps.CompEquippableAbilityReloadable.cooldownGerund>冷却中</RI_Weapon_GlassPearlUmbrella.comps.CompEquippableAbilityReloadable.cooldownGerund>
  <!-- EN: 伞柄 -->
  <RI_Weapon_GlassPearlUmbrella.tools.0.label>伞柄</RI_Weapon_GlassPearlUmbrella.tools.0.label>
  <!-- EN: 伞面 -->
  <RI_Weapon_GlassPearlUmbrella.tools.1.label>伞面</RI_Weapon_GlassPearlUmbrella.tools.1.label>
  
  <!-- EN: PoJun sword【First-rate】 -->
  <RI_Weapon_PojunSword.label>破军剑【一品】</RI_Weapon_PojunSword.label>
  <!-- EN: 【First-rate】Melee weapon\n\nThis sword is a replica of a famous sword from ancient times. -->
  <RI_Weapon_PojunSword.description>【一品】近战兵器\n\n这把剑是古代一名著名的佩剑的复制版。据说他曾经驾驭飞剑，独自一人突入千人大军中，刹那间生灵涂炭，他在斩杀百余人后为后续部队撕开了防线，力竭而亡。为了纪念他，他的配剑被作为一种象征，流传下来。</RI_Weapon_PojunSword.description>
  <!-- EN: 破军飞剑 -->
  <RI_Weapon_PojunSword.comps.CompEquippableAbilityReloadable.chargeNoun>破军飞剑</RI_Weapon_PojunSword.comps.CompEquippableAbilityReloadable.chargeNoun>
