  <!-- EN: 【First-rate】Melee weapon\n\nA mysterious sword, which is said to be the first weapon used by the celestial gods to kill their own kind. After loading the spiritual crystal, you can unleash a strike that will kill any creature. -->
  <RI_Weapon_SlayinglmmortalSword.description>【一品】近战兵器\n\n一把玄妙宝剑，据说是最早的天仙用来屠戮同类的兵器。在装填灵石后，可以释放出一次足以斩杀任何生灵的斩击。</RI_Weapon_SlayinglmmortalSword.description>
